市場均衡とパレート効率性について

Economies without production are considered and the relation between competitive market equilibria and Pareto efficient allocations of resources is explained.
第5回 厚生経済学の基本定理[ Fundamental theorems of welfare economics ]
市場機構の有効性について

The relation between competitive market equilibria and Pareto efficient allocations of resources is explained.
